    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821310/extras/1b101b973926b3da790ca4ff51a008ee.apng?t=1742289685\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821310/extras/1b101b973926b3da790ca4ff51a008ee.poster.avif?t=1742289685\" class=\"bb_img\" width=640 height=128 /></picture></span><br><strong>帮助小橘猫夺回她最爱的纸箱!</strong>在这个紧凑平台游戏中小橘猫将通过敏捷的动作勇敢面对各种场景挑战，将遇到形形色色可爱的怪物以及最后与宿敌一决胜负！<br>这款2D平台游戏采用了90年代早期的美术风格。扮演小橘猫奔跑、跳跃和踩踏来通过不同的关卡。<br>收集小鱼儿来获得高分并且在速通模式中与全世界的小橘猫一决高低。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>四个可爱但充满挑战的世界等待着你！</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>图像和音乐带着90年代掌机游戏的味道。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>超过30个手工打造的关卡，充满了可爱的怪物，以及小橘猫的一生宿敌！</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821310/extras/568e644b356b0b64919ac9b2a33ec7e3.apng?t=1742289685\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1821310/extras/568e644b356b0b64919ac9b2a33ec7e3.poster.avif?t=1742289685\" class=\"bb_img\" width=640 height=180 /></picture></span>",
